Before making a release the following have to be done:

1. Update version number in configure.in
2. Update version number in traffic.spec
3. Update README
4. Update CHANGELOG
5. Commit everything to CVS
6. Export everything into a new directory.
7. Rename new directory to traffic-VERSION
8. tar cvzf traffic-VERSION.tgz traffic-VERSION/*
9. zip -r9 traffic-VERSION.zip traffic-VERSION/*
10. su
11. copy traffic-VERSION.tgz to /usr/src/RPM/SOURCES
12. rpm -ba traffic.spec
13. Go to Windows and using Borland Builder Build the code
14. Go to InstallShield and build the distribution
15. Go to PackageForTheWeb and build Traffic-VERSION.exe
16. Upload to upload.sourceforge.net/incoming the .zip .tgz .rpm .src.rpm
.exe files.
17. Do release on sourceforge and freshmeat
